==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Undeify
<hw>Un*de"i*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>deify</ets>.]</ety> <def>To degrade from the state
of deity; to deprive of the character or qualities of a god; to deprive
of the reverence due to a god.</def> <rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Undeniable</ent>⟦br⟧
